FCBPW MISSION Providing opportunities for women in the workplace to come
    together for bible-based worship, fellowship, discipleship, and
    encouragement, advancing the spread of the gospel for the Glory of
    God. FCBPW
VISION Reaching and inspiring women in workplaces everywhere to know the
love of Christ and grow in grace and the knowledge of God. Bringing women together to build relationships; teaching,
encouraging, and equipping them for works of service to the building up of the
body of Christ. All this for the glory of God! STATEMENT OF FAITH We believe the Bible is the inspired and inerrant Word of God. We believe in one God; Father, Son and Holy Spirit. We believe that we are saved by grace through faith and that is not of
    ourselves, it is the gift of God. We believe Jesus Christ is the Son of God, that he died for our sins and
    was raised from the dead, and that whoever believes in Him will have
    everlasting life. CALENDAR OF EVENTS FCBPW holds bi-monthly luncheon meetings in which a business or professional
leader gives their testimony and encourages women to share their faith in the
workplace. Meetings are held at the Town & Country Club from 11:30
a.m.  1:00 p.m. Be sure to check back for more information regarding upcoming 
programs in 2007! Map
    & Directions to Town
    & Country Club SMALL GROUP
BIBLE STUDIES FCBPW also holds monthly bible studies in Minneapolis and Saint Paul and
plans to expand in other cities as the organization grows. If you are interested in joining a small group, please call: Minneapolis: Sherry Meyer ( 612)
376-9361 St. Paul: Sherry Hastings (651) 291-3576 Women's Club: Carla
    Pedersen (612) 752-1917 Woodbury: Nancy Branton (651) 459-0528 NEWSLETTER

INFORMATION The Fellowship of Christian Business & Professional Women (FCBPW) is excited
to announce the launch of our new membership initiative. This 12-month
membership will begin on the date we receive payment and will continue for 12
months.  The annual
membership fee of $75.00 will
enable FCBPW to more effectively reach out to business and professional women in
the Twin Cities area.  Please review the benefits listed below that are
included with your $75 membership fee, and prayerfully consider becoming a
member. Click
here to print and complete an application. Benefits of Membership Receive
    all FCBPW mailings, including the quarterly electronic newsletter. Opportunity
    to be featured in FCBPW's quarterly newsletter under Member Profiles. Be
    included in, and receive, the annual FCBPW Membership Directory. Be
    eligible to volunteer for FCBPW committee opportunities and Board positions. Criteria for Membership Agreement
    and acceptance of FCBPW's mission, vision, values and statement of faith. Successful
    completion of the Application for Membership. Membership
Expectations and Fees Help
    promote FCBPW to business and professional women. Encourage
    and support one another. Annual
    Membership Fee is $75.00.  Membership dues pay for 12-month membership
    from date payment is received. Aportion of your membership dues may be tax
    deductible. Consult your tax
    advisor for more information. We hope you will prayerfully consider becoming a member of FCBPW and helping
to support our mission. Click
here to print and complete an application. CONTACT
